videos.headline: Eastern Michigan's Sexton climbs ladder for 75-yard TD
videos.description: Tyler Wiegers slightly underthrows the ball, but Mathew Sexton comes back to outleap his defender before running for a TD.

videos.headline: Eastern Michigan gets on the board with 75-yard TD pass
videos.description: Tyler Wiegers slightly underthrows the ball, but Mathew Sexton comes back to outleap his defender before running for a TD.

videos.headline: Moore reverses for 53-yard gain
videos.description: Purdue's Rondale Moore takes the handoff and then reverses for a big gain.

videos.headline: Purdue scores with shovel pass
videos.description: Elijah Sindelar tosses a quick shovel pass to Markell Jones for a 7-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Knox shows patience on 45-yard Purdue TD
videos.description: D.J. Knox finds a hole and runs for a 45-yard touchdown to put Purdue ahead 19-17.
